# Overview

Welcome to Diane Benites's Personal Website! This website was coded by Diane Benites using R Markdown. Throughout this website you can learn more about my interests, academic background, and professional experiences. 


## About Me

My name is Diane and I'm a second year MPH student at the Mailman School of Public Health. I'm studying Sociomedical Sciences, with a certificate in Applied Biostatistics and Public Health Data Science.
